#git fetch/pull
1) go to the github and go to your repo
2) take the https url and do the git clone

git clone <httpsurl>

3) cd <reponame>

example
 git clone https://github.com/amitopenwriteup/mystartraining.git
 cd mystarttraining
 
 4) git status
 
 5) now go to the github and add one new file into your repo
 6) go to linux box to your local git repo
 git fetch origin main
 git status
 
 #one commit behind from origin/main
 7) git pull origin main
 git status
 
